## Summary
This documentation details the Behavioral Cohorts API which allows developers to list, export, and upload cohorts in Amplitude, with specific endpoints for getting all cohorts, requesting a single cohort, checking request status, downloading cohort data, uploading new cohorts, and incrementally updating cohort membership.

